Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.82,0:00:09.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 回想一下和我的练习
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.36,0:00:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的身体应该已经记住该如何行动了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.10,0:01:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}第15话\N捉迷藏的小奏鸣曲\N～sonatine～
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.94,0:02:15.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.07,0:02:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要这样继续坚持住的话
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.63,0:02:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一定会来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.04,0:02:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一只怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.13,0:02:51.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.10,0:02:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:56.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样就只剩一只了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.23,0:03:00.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有哪里疼吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.55,0:03:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这块痕记是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.44,0:03:08.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.68,0:03:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用不上力气
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.81,0:03:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.57,0:03:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是妖魔的诅咒吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.04,0:03:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从最近开始就是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.68,0:03:18.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 刚才没有现在那么严重
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去医院吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.93,0:03:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天就到此为止
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:28.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你都动不了的话 其它事就不用谈了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.95,0:03:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算过段时间 我想它也只会恶化下去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.87,0:03:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.82,0:03:38.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.52,0:03:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到这里就行了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是第一次半夜来这里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.22,0:03:50.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下来要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.69,0:03:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么都不用做
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.72,0:03:57.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你待在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.36,0:04:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一在我身边的话 可以当诱饵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.36,0:04:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.01,0:04:08.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这种情况 你还能说出这种话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.60,0:04:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.27,0:04:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是诱饵还是饲料我都会为你做的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.73,0:04:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你暂时就给我乖乖待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总感觉像是在玩捉迷藏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:28.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,捉迷藏…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.84,0:04:31.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小时候玩过么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.29,0:04:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像这样忍住呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.96,0:04:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后一动不动地等着鬼来找自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.48,0:04:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有玩过
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.39,0:04:41.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和佐祐理学姐么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久之前 曾经有过一个朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.42,0:04:50.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那个孩子…也从我身边逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.70,0:04:53.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.83,0:04:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待着别动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.22,0:04:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说什么傻话 你还不能动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:04:59.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要利用高度
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:15.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.30,0:05:16.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.91,0:05:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样乱来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.69,0:05:21.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失败了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:31.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:34.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.92,0:05:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.00,0:05:41.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的目标是我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:43.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就让我来当你对手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟上来吧 怪物
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.95,0:05:46.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.26,0:05:50.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 到后院去
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.66,0:05:51.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后院？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.77,0:06:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样子可不是光退学就了事的了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.97,0:06:31.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:33.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么想说的话就说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.52,0:06:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.41,0:06:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你真的有话要对我说
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.91,0:06:59.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后院
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.96,0:07:02.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底有什么
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.04,0:07:06.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞 你一直让人琢磨不透
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.65,0:07:08.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沉默寡言
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.92,0:07:10.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对别人的感受也很迟钝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.78,0:07:12.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又任性 还让人担心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 一定要有人陪在你身边
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.79,0:08:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吆 舞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.44,0:08:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吆 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.16,0:08:34.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.96,0:08:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,振作一点 舞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.89,0:08:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.08,0:08:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 你要胡来到什么地步啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.65,0:08:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想吃牛肉盖浇饭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.23,0:08:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.71,0:08:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为被破坏的更厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.63,0:09:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才那些都是幻觉吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.75,0:09:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.25,0:09:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.72,0:09:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去买 你给我乖乖地待着
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.08,0:09:09.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完之后马上去医院
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.19,0:09:15.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子饿了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.62,0:09:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里等我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.61,0:09:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我马上就回来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用太着急
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.31,0:09:35.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起 舞就可以做回普通的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.77,0:09:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以这份牛肉盖浇饭 本应是一份微薄的贺礼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.67,0:09:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞 我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.02,0:09:44.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.77,0:09:47.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.92,0:09:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还剩下一只吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.84,0:09:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙 为了能让我逃走…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.85,0:10:06.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.39,0:10:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用我能听懂的话说出来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:16.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是最后剩下的妖魔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.14,0:10:24.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.74,0:10:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.29,0:10:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.79,0:10:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 动物园 舞没去过吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兔子先生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.48,0:10:51.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有啊 还有长颈鹿先生 狮子先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:52.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连猩猩先生也有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.44,0:10:56.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等妈妈病好了就带你去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:10:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.04,0:11:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 我们约好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:01.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:09.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 没事吧 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.94,0:11:28.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很努力地拿来了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.34,0:11:28.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我就做个好东西给你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.00,0:11:44.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是兔子先生啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.83,0:12:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.06,0:12:05.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又疼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.86,0:12:08.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.30,0:12:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在去动物园吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.36,0:12:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天身体感觉还不错 我们去看长颈鹿还有猩猩先生吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.91,0:12:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 医生会生气的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.17,0:12:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是很想去动物园的吗 舞
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.72,0:12:24.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.95,0:12:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.04,0:12:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈从来不骗人的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.72,0:12:34.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有今天了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.03,0:12:37.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动物园在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.36,0:12:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出了医院之后坐巴士 然后再换电车就到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:45.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很远吗 要花几分钟能到
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 大约一小时左右吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.44,0:12:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事 真的没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.94,0:12:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.96,0:13:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一会儿… 就稍微让我休息一会儿
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.09,0:13:10.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 我们还是回房吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.90,0:13:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的 只要休息会的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.64,0:13:19.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈也很想和舞一起去动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.61,0:13:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.72,0:13:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 舞 我好像睡着了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.48,0:13:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.19,0:13:42.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过妈妈 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.80,0:13:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是动物园哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.28,0:13:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞和妈妈的…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.33,0:13:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 好漂亮的动物园
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.57,0:13:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈 又疼了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.00,0:14:01.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.10,0:14:03.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不疼了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.10,0:14:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快好起来 妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:19.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你 求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.22,0:14:37.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会来了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.46,0:15:29.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.97,0:15:33.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是舞还是舞的能力 都能全部接受的人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:37.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部？ 他不会怕舞吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.89,0:15:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会害怕的 因为他是个很坚强的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.55,0:15:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是来玩的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.41,0:15:59.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 只是迷路了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.25,0:16:03.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 你太慢了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:06.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞太矮了 都看不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.98,0:16:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.65,0:16:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兔子先生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是让我的 这样就比较好找了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:36.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我因为有这个能力而无法待在原来的城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.45,0:16:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 正因为有这个能力 你才能治好你妈妈的病吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.44,0:16:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话是这么说没错
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.06,0:16:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天 你会喜欢上自己这个力量的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.46,0:17:00.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天暑假就结束了 我一定要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.99,0:17:02.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你帮帮我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.60,0:17:04.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我帮你 帮什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.10,0:17:06.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔来了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.81,0:17:07.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.88,0:17:11.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对 妖魔来了啊 就在我们一直玩的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.53,0:17:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我们两个人一起保护它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.15,0:17:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会回来的 到时候两个人再一起玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.23,0:17:22.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的来了 我一个人是保护不了的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.30,0:17:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会等你的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.41,0:17:30.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使一个人我也会战斗的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.70,0:17:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 总有一天你一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.71,0:18:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一 快出去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.01,0:18:03.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在的我 是保护不了你的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.37,0:18:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞 其实并没有什么妖魔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.04,0:18:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一开始就不存在
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.79,0:18:12.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔…是你自己制造出来的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.80,0:18:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由你的能力实体化出来的产物
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不懂你在说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.12,0:18:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每当你打倒妖魔时 你自身会受到伤害就是这个原因
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.00,0:18:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔…不 你的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.69,0:18:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有事要告诉我 只是由于力量过于强大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.74,0:18:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使我无法了解它们想要传达给我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.32,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后只剩一只的时候 我终于理解了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你小时候由于不想失去朋友 而编造了妖魔来了的谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.97,0:18:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后强迫自己去相信这个谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.26,0:18:50.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是自己想要去相信这个谎言
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.84,0:18:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当时那个朋友就是我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.18,0:18:56.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们曾经见过 在很久之前
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.25,0:19:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那时候的男孩 因为害怕我而逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.83,0:19:02.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和其他人一样
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.63,0:19:07.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是因为暑假结束了 所以不得不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.70,0:19:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之后的一年 我又去了那片麦田
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.00,0:19:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经见不到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.72,0:19:17.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这十年里 一个人守护着这个地方呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.15,0:19:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些都是实话
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.27,0:19:23.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:26.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今天起你就做回那时候的舞吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.32,0:19:30.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你能接受自己的能力 战斗就会结束
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.06,0:19:33.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖魔想要传达给我的就是这个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:35.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑笑吧 舞
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:37.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像以前一样…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.45,0:19:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了一个很长的梦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.57,0:19:42.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经不用再战斗了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.31,0:19:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把剑舍弃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.58,0:19:46.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法舍弃剑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.42,0:19:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我一直都是依靠它而活下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.72,0:19:53.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 舍弃掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.64,0:19:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要舍弃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.07,0:19:58.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舍弃剑的我 会变得很脆弱的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:20:01.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会给祐一还有佐祐理添很多麻烦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那有什么关系
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.52,0:20:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和佐祐理学姐 都最喜欢你了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.56,0:20:21.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你 祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.37,0:20:26.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 很谢谢你…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.06,0:20:38.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.67,0:20:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞 不要死
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.62,0:20:44.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.49,0:20:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个…这个笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.28,0:20:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祐一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.64,0:21:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 我来晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.89,0:21:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系 你还是来见我了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.25,0:21:09.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这次 你不会再离开了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.53,0:21:13.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为我们是朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.13,0:21:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意接受我当你的朋友吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.21,0:21:18.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请你不要害怕舞
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.96,0:21:19.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一言为定
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.47,0:21:27.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤口…在愈合
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.98,0:21:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你救了她的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.44,0:21:34.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想 现在一定能够回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.03,0:21:36.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想能够被接受了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.25,0:21:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是 舞的…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.02,0:21:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是舞的能力的残片
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我希望你能这么叫我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.32,0:21:48.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞 起床了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.61,0:22:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舞 是时候该从梦里醒过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.76,0:23:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们两位都还是老样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.65,0:23:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等有空 就出去玩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:49.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不嫌弃的话 可以陪你一整天哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.48,0:23:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得那时候的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.40,0:24:01.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋子阿姨她… 秋子阿姨她…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.01,0:24:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能有足够的时间 这样待在一起就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.09,0:24:10.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一个想去的地方 行吗
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.44,0:24:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs26}{\fad(300,0)}第16话\N真夜中的圣谭曲\N～oratorio～
